{"tid":1064102,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"強掛五星旗！周董、子瑜登亞太百大帥哥美女　遭變「支那人」","createTime":"2019-03-16T09:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T08:07:46.000Z","uid":60286,"like":17,"dislike":190,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"91ec871c983fa3f494132b1063c8b937884f712b","tid":1064102,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"美國電影網站《TC Candler》每年都會公布「世界百大最美臉孔」，排行榜每年都會引發全球網友熱議，去年Twice台灣成員周子瑜都拿下第二名，今日該網站公布「亞太區百大美女排行榜」、「亞太區百大帥哥排行榜」，子瑜竟只拿下第四名，國籍還遭大會掛上五星旗。<br />\n <br />\n《TC Candler》今日公布「亞太區百大最美臉孔排行榜」，當中許多台灣籍藝人入選，其中Twicw台灣女孩周子瑜、歐陽娜娜、鬼鬼、周杰倫、彭于晏等人都入選百大最美臉孔，但他們的照片右上角竟然都被掛著五星旗，強制被大會改成中國籍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLVzmXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLVzmXz.jpg&h=cd96bbb9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wS57GXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwS57GXA.jpg&h=b35cd4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，周子瑜去年獲選「2018全球最美臉蛋」第2名時，照片右上角顯示的是台灣國旗，先前公布入選名單時，就被網友發現台灣籍藝人清一色被掛上五星旗，引起台灣網友抗議，呼籲主辦單位盡速修正。"},{"pid":"cd1a163a64b35035f3f8cdc53b71a4b2b4e9df02","tid":1064102,"uid":3962,"like":177,"dislike":2,"score":175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲明星為左搵錢自己都唔care奶共班豬腦fans反而care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0919b1bc1ba5b598ce7d3e3a31a4da61da213dc7","tid":1064102,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"解解30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13d95058c2515fec75f59fda6c8ef67af2c1d36","tid":1064102,"uid":74065,"like":200,"dislike":46,"score":154,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2Ez6uM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2Ez6uM.jpg&h=d3cfec2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n心甘情願架WO"},{"pid":"f6